title: Did Jim Morrison Fake His Death? - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 7/9/21
itunes:title: Did Jim Morrison Fake His Death? - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 7/9/21
description:
Guest host Ian Punnett and music historian Michael Christopher discuss the anomalies involved in the death of Doors singer Jim Morrison from a drug overdose in Paris in 1971, and whether Morrison faked his own death to escape the rock n roll limelight.
